<th colspan="2" style="text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color: lightgrey">Heart failure</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center"><a href="/wiki/File:Heartfailure.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Heartfailure.jpg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/99/Heartfailure.jpg/230px-Heartfailure.jpg" width="230" height="305" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/99/Heartfailure.jpg/345px-Heartfailure.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/99/Heartfailure.jpg 2x" data-file-width="377" data-file-height="500" /></a>
<div>The major signs and symptoms of heart failure</div>
</td>
