а</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-hu"><a href="//hu.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sz%C3%ADvel%C3%A9gtelens%C3%A9g" title="Szívelégtelenség – Hungarian" lang="hu" hreflang="hu">Magyar</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-mk"><a href="//mk.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A1%D1%80%D1%86%D0%B5%D0%B2%D0%B0_%D1%81%D0%BB%D0%B0%D0%B1%D0%BE%D1%81%D1%82" title="Срцева слабост – Macedonian" lang="mk" hreflang="mk">Македонски</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ms"><a href="//ms.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kegagalan_jantung" title="Kegagalan jantung – Malay" lang="ms" hreflang="ms">Bahasa Melayu</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-nl"><a href="//nl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hartfalen" title="Hartfalen – Dutch" lang="nl" hreflang="nl">Nederlands</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ja"><a href="//ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%BF%83%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%A8" title="心不全 – Japanese" lang="ja" hreflang="ja">日本語</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-no"><a href="//no.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hjertesvikt" title="Hjertesvikt – Norwegian" lang="no" hreflang="no">Norsk bokmål</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-nn"><a href="//nn.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hjartesvikt" title="Hjartesvikt – Norwegian Nynorsk" lang="nn" hreflang="nn">Norsk nynorsk</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-or"><a href="//or.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E0%AC%B9%E0%AD%83%E0%AC%A6%E0%AD%8D%E2%80%8C%E0%AC%AA%E0%AC%BE%E0%AC%A4" title="ହୃଦ୍‌ପାତ – Oriya" lang="or" hreflang="or">ଓଡ଼ିଆ</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ps"><a href="//ps.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D8%B2%DA%93%D9%87_%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%A8%D8%B1%DB%8C" title="زړه نابری – Pashto" lang="ps" hreflang="ps">پښتو</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-pl"><a href="//pl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Niewydolno%C5%9B%C4%87_serca" title="Niewydolność serca – Polish" lang="pl" hreflang="pl">Polski</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-pt"><a href="//pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Insufici%C3%AAncia_card%C3%ADaca" title="Insuficiência cardíaca – Portuguese" lang="pt" hreflang="pt">Português</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ro"><a href="//ro.wikipedia.org/wiki/Insuficien%C8%9B%C4%83_cardiac%C4%83" title="Insuficiență cardiacă – Romanian" lang="ro" hreflang="ro">Română</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ru"><a href="//ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A1%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B4%D0%B5%D1%87%D0%BD%D0%B0%D1%8F_%D0%BD%D0%B5%D0%B4%D0%BE%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B0%D1%82%D0%BE%D1%87%D0%BD%D0%BE%D1%81%D1%82%D1%8C" title="Сердечная недостаточность – Russian" lang="ru" hreflang="ru">Русский</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-simple"><a href="//simple.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heart_failure" title="Heart failure – Simple English" lang="simple" hreflang="simple">Simple English</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-sl"><a href="//sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sr%C4%8Dno_popu%C5%A1%C4%8Danje" title="Srčno popuščanje – Slovenian" lang="sl" hreflang="sl">Slovenščina</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ckb"><a href="//ckb.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D8%B3%D8%B3%D8%AA%D8%A8%D9%88%D9%88%D9%86%DB%8C_%D8%AF%DA%B5" title="سستبوونی دڵ – Central Kurdish" lang="ckb" hreflang="ckb">کوردیی ناوەندی</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-sr"><a href="//sr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zatajenje_srca" title="Zatajenje srca – Serbian" lang="sr" hreflang="sr">Српски / srpski</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-sh"><a href="//sh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zatajenje_srca" title="Zatajenje srca – Serbo-Croatian" lang="sh" hreflang="sh">Srpskohrvatski / српскохрватски</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-fi"><a href="//fi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Syd%C3%A4men_vajaatoiminta" title="Sydämen vajaatoiminta – Finnish" lang="fi" hreflang="fi">Suomi</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-sv"><a href="//sv.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hj%C3%A4rtsvikt" title="Hjärtsvikt – Swedish" lang="sv" hreflang="sv">Svenska</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-tl"><a href="//tl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pagpalya_ng_puso" title="Pagpa